	width 10cm

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
We have chosen Jobindex, because it includes not only the portal's own job
 postings, but also almost all publicly available job posting from other
 job portals and companies' webpages.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Unlike some other job portals, Jobindex does not have a filter for 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

remote
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 job postings.
 Therefore, we identify the listings by defining a list of keywords, that
 we assume would be mentioned in a posting offering the option of working
 from home either part time or full time:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\align center
